ygData.messageBody:
Batfang headband - West Karana ogres. No for level 15. Need a low-mid 30's
party
Crested Helm - Mistmoore Not attainable. Not sure on the level, but you
need a party of 20's to take on the yard trash there

Whirling Bloodstone and whirling malachite - Evil Eyes in Beholder. If you
pull together a full party you could probably take on the eyes. Be careful
though. they have nasty magics
